BEGIN

INPUT infix expression

REVERSE the infix expression

FOR each character ch in expression DO
    IF ch is '(' THEN
        Replace it with ')'
    ELSE IF ch is ')' THEN
        Replace it with '('
END FOR

CALL infixToPostfix on modified expression
STORE result in postfix

REVERSE postfix
STORE result as prefix

DISPLAY prefix

END



Infix to prefix
